  <brief_title>Titratable Dosing in Moderate to Severe Asthmatics</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 52 wk Randomized, Doubleblind, Single Dummy, Parallel Group Multicenter Phase 3 Study Comparing the Long Term Safety of Symbicort pMDI 4x160/4.5mcg Bid to SymbicortpMDI 2x160/4.5mcg Bid &amp; Budesonide HFA pMDI 4x160mcg Bid in Adult and Adolescent Subjects With Asthma</official_title>
